1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,876
Here is one useful thing to watch for.

2
00:00:02,826 --> 00:00:06,613
Forgetting the equals sign is the most common slip.

3
00:00:06,613 --> 00:00:09,565
Every formula must start with =.

4
00:00:09,565 --> 00:00:14,184
If it happens, pause, reset, and try again calmly.

